fields.description:
I was trying to use the Console on IE11.  Eucaconsole does not load properly.  It appears as though there is a method to getting IE11 to run in the latest mode since some versions of IE11 may not run sites that way.  There is a meta tag that forces IE11 to do this.
{code}
<meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge;" />
{code}
It might be a good idea to include that in our code in case other IE users run into this same problem.  I have attached a screenshot of how the console loads on IE11 using the wrong mode.
